'''Ismahane Lahmar''' (yavutse 25 Ukwakira 1982), ni umukinnyi wa filimi ukomoka muri [[Tunisiya]] akaba aba mu [[Bufaransa]]  . Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa filimi ngufi zizwi cyane  ''Rainbow'', ''WOH!'' and ''Breaking News'' .<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm5830683/</ref><ref>https://artify.tn/en/professional/5e78db8c42e5ad24cf7497fe</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 25 Ukwakira 1982 i [[Paris|Paris mu]] [[Bufaransa]], avukira ku babyeyi bo muri [[Tunisiya|Tuniziya]]. Icyakora, yimukiye muri [[Tuniziya]] amaze kuvuka, abana na sekuru kugeza afite imyaka umunani. Hanyuma asubira mu Bufaransa. <ref name="cinematunisien">` http://cinematunisien.com/2020/02/20/ismahane-lahmar/</ref> <ref name="meditalents">http://meditalents.net/ismahane-lahmar/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Amaze gusubira mu [[Bufaransa]], yiyandikishije muri kaminuza ya Paris XII yiga ibijyanye n'ubukungu. <ref name="meditalents">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[http://meditalents.net/ismahane-lahmar/ "Ismahane Lahmar: life"]. meditalents<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">13 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> Amaze kurangiza icyiciro cya Economics and Management, yimukiye kwiga indimi z'amahanga hamwe na mushiki we. Hagati y'umwaka wa kaminuza, yagiye mu rugendo muri [[Kanada]] maze yifatanya n'inshuti y'umuririmbyi mu ruzinduko rwa Quebec. Muri kiriya gihe, yatangiye kuyobora film. <ref name="cinematunisien">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[http://cinematunisien.com/2020/02/20/ismahane-lahmar/ "Ismahane Lahmar"]. cinematunisien<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">13 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

Yahuguye gukina  mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Audiovisual Production (ESRA) i Paris. Nyuma yaje kwimukira muri kaminuza ya New York abona impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga mu kuyobora. Muri 2008, yerekanwe bwa mbere muri firime  ngufi ya ''Red Hope'' muri 2008. Yanditse  yerekana amashusho ya ''Al Yasmine'' abifashijwemo namahugurwa ya Dubai Film Connection. <ref>http://africultures.com/personnes/?no=35845&utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=480</ref>

Mu mwaka wa 2010, yahisemo kujya muri [[Tuniziya]], hamwe na filime iri ''Under the Elbow'' . Icyakora, yakuyeho icyemezo kubera imvururu za politiki mu gihugu. Mu 2014, we filimi ya kabiri ngufi  ''Rainbow.'' Yatanzwe muri Nyakanga 2014 kuri Rares & Tunisiens Cycle. <ref name="cinematunisien">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[http://cinematunisien.com/2020/02/20/ismahane-lahmar/ "Ismahane Lahmar"]. cinematunisien<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">13 November</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> Mu mwaka wa 2016, yanditse kandi ayobora filime ''Woh'', urwenya rwo muri [[Tuniziya]] rwatewe inkunga n'abaturage ba [[Tuniziya]]. Muri 2019 yashinze isosiyete ikora 'Madame Prod' aho ateza imbere akanashyigikira imishinga y'abagore na sinema. <ref>https://artify.tn/professional/5e78db8c42e5ad24cf7497fe</ref>

